~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

============= ================================== ==========================================
Extension     Configure switch(es)               Remarks
============= ================================== ==========================================
_`bcmath`     --enable-bcmath
_`bz2`        --with-bz2
_`gd`         --with-gd --with-freetype-dir=/usr
              --with-jpeg-dir=/usr --with-ttf
              --with-xpm-dir --with-png-dir
              --with-jpeg-dir --with-t1lib
