Extensions that are not bundled with PHP
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

============= =============================================================================
Extension     Configure switch(es)
============= =============================================================================
_`apc`        You need to install the `APC extension`_ through PECL.
_`fileinfo`   You need to install the `fileinfo extension`_ through PECL.

